Cooking can be fun with CSFML.
The goal of the game is to buy the ingredients, to know the recipes and cook them as quickly as possible before the customer leaves!
If you do not serve a customer before he gets fed up, he'll leave and you'll lose money...
Be careful not to go below 0 pieces!

USAGE
	./my_cook <limit value>
	The limit value is the maximum cash value before the game ends
USER INTERACTIONS
	Mouse : select recipes
	UP scrolling up into the menu
	DOWN scrolling down into the menu
	ENTER select option into the menu
	ESC option menu
